e":"The Expendables 2","video":false,"overview":"Mr. Church reunites the Expendables for what should be an easy paycheck, but when one of their men is murdered on the job, their quest for revenge puts them deep in enemy territory and up against an unexpected threat.","genre_ids":[28,12,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.3484,"vote_count":7058,"poster_path":"/74rTIGyGoIu5KSxDVMdr8H3MtMo.jpg","release_date":"2012-08-08","vote_average":6.348,"backdrop_path":"/ihKsZZYMbyHXC1L7s90WDLITdC5.jpg","original_title":"The Expendables 2","original_language":"en"},{"id":49026,"adult":false,"title":"The Dark Knight Rises","video":false,"overview":"Following the death of District Attorney Harvey Dent, Batman assumes responsibility for Dent's crimes to protect the late attorney's reputation and is subsequently hunted by the Gotham City Police Department. Eight years later, Batman encounters the mysterious Selina Kyle and the villainous Bane, a new terrorist leader who overwhelms Gotham's finest. The Dark Knight resurfaces to protect a city that has branded him an enemy.","genre_ids":[28,80,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":15.4056,"vote_count":24020,"poster_path":"/hr0L2aueqlP2BYUblTTjmtn0hw4.jpg","release_date":"2012-07-17","vote_average":7.791,"backdrop_path":"/y2DB71C4nyIdMrANijz8mzvQtk6.jpg","original_title":"The Dark Knight Rises","original_language":"en"},{"id":70160,"adult":false,"title":"The Hunger Games","video":false,"overview":"In a dystopian society where the Capitol forces each district to send two young tributes to fight to the death in a televised spectacle, a girl volunteers to take her sister’s place, setting the stage for a struggle of survival and defiance.","genre_ids":[878,12,28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.0462,"vote_count":23027,"poster_path":"/yXCbOiVDCxO71zI7cuwBRXdftq8.jpg","release_date":"2012-03-12","vote_average":7.221,"backdrop_path":"/3sndNmvdF0R8AeyCmVoNv8LKtNy.jpg","original_title":"The Hunger Games","original_language":"en"},{