o in him must emerge if he is to save the world from annihilation and become the symbol of hope for all mankind.","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":9.7733,"vote_count":15956,"poster_path":"/8GFtkImmK0K1VaUChR0n9O61CFU.jpg","release_date":"2013-06-12","vote_average":6.639,"backdrop_path":"/69EFgWWPFWbRNHmQgYdSnyJ94Ge.jpg","original_title":"Man of Steel","original_language":"en"},{"id":500,"adult":false,"title":"Reservoir Dogs","video":false,"overview":"A botched robbery indicates a police informant, and the pressure mounts in the aftermath at a warehouse. Crime begets violence as the survivors -- veteran Mr. White, newcomer Mr. Orange, psychopathic parolee Mr. Blonde, bickering weasel Mr. Pink and Nice Guy Eddie -- unravel.","genre_ids":[80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.6012,"vote_count":15173,"poster_path":"/xi8Iu6qyTfyZVDVy60raIOYJJmk.jpg","release_date":"1992-09-02","vote_average":8.117,"backdrop_path":"/jwt159hXWA9Q5xpBo8hWb3zwLi7.jpg","original_title":"Reservoir Dogs","original_language":"en"},{"id":157336,"adult":false,"title":"Interstellar","video":false,"overview":"The adventures of a group of explorers who make use of a newly discovered wormhole to surpass the limitations on human space travel and conquer the vast distances involved in an interstellar voyage.","genre_ids":[12,18,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":45.3727,"vote_count":38953,"poster_path":"/gEU2QniE6E77NI6lCU6MxlNBvIx.jpg","release_date":"2014-11-05","vote_average":8.5,"backdrop_path":"/2ssWTSVklAEc98frZUQhgtGHx7s.jpg","original_title":"Interstellar","original_language":"en"},{"id":106646,"adult":false,"title":"The Wolf of Wall Street","video":false,"overview":"A New York stockbroker refuses to cooperate in a large securities fraud case involving corruption on Wall Street, corporate banking world and mob infiltration. Based on Jordan Belfort's autobiography.","genre_ids":[80,18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":16.6756,"vote_count":25533,"poster_path":