oceans to capture or destroy the enemy, though he must weigh his commitment to duty and ferocious pursuit of glory against the safety of his devoted crew, including the ship's thoughtful surgeon, his best friend.","genre_ids":[12,18,10752],"popularity":3.6584,"vote_count":3437,"poster_path":"/s1cVTQEZYn4nSjZLnFbzLP0j8y2.jpg","release_date":"2003-11-14","vote_average":7.181,"backdrop_path":"/zMHyNxNt4zhL939XX8QLBW3gWfu.jpg","original_title":"Master and Commander: The Far Side of the World","original_language":"en"},{"id":277702,"adult":false,"title":"Supremacy","video":false,"overview":"The story centers on paroled white supremacist who has just killed a cop, and takes a black family hostage. Within hours of being released from 14 years of solitary confinement in maximum-security Pelican Bay State Prison, Garrett Tully is on the run again. When he finds a house off a dirt road and takes a family hostage, he thinks the Aryan Brotherhood has his back–and his kidnap victims are black. The family’s patriarch, Mr. Walker, is a jaded ex-con who hates cops so much he disavowed his own son for becoming one. Seeing a familiar desperation in Tully, Walker refuses to call the authorities for help, causing familial tensions to escalate, and soon grave missteps are made.","genre_ids":[80,18],"popularity":2.9748,"vote_count":63,"poster_path":"/jyuFA9AYBLNJY4Zb2Q5ty8cSIbW.jpg","release_date":"2014-06-12","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/92emBazocuGHWg8qWEAYOfbvZE5.jpg","original_title":"Supremacy","original_language":"en"},{"id":471616,"adult":false,"title":"Indian Horse","video":false,"overview":"Follows the life of Native Canadian Saul Indian Horse as he survives residential school and life amongst the racism of the 1970s. A talented hockey player, Saul must find his own path as he battles stereotypes and alcoholism.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.5887,"vote_count":76,"poster_path":"/6PRmK9svHolvZ2CLNoBkmViYlrB.jpg","release_date":"2018-04-13","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/3An5TOYitpGnZWU3GhLGVKI4vcA.jpg","original_title":"Indian Horse","original_language":"en"},{"id":661996,"adult":false,"title":"Un Hombre Violento","video":false,"overview":"Bent on avenging the death of his gambling addicted father, Julian Carrera embarks on a violent spree with deadly consequences.","genre_ids":[28,80,18,53],"popularity":0.1719,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/wOw0EtETlLyqcDG1Xq3GtaZWj3F.jpg","release_date":"1984-01-01","vote_average":4.2,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Un Hombre Violento","original_language":"es"},{"id":471689,"adult":false,"title":"Everything Is Free","video":false,"overview":"Ivan is a US painter residing in Colombia. His best friend, Christian, and younger brother, Cole, come to visit. Somewhere along the way, Ivan and Cole hit it off although Cole is not gay. Will older brother Christian be okay with that?","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":0.5461,"vote_count":26,"poster_path":"/u1GV3ULs7i4LnetwweOxesXkfaK.jpg","release_date":"2017-09-03","vote_average":5.1,"backdrop_path":"/nyi66GPJnN1Q93iOzwmk5oftPze.jpg","original_title":"Everything Is Free","original_language":"en"},{"id":1259448,"adult":false,"title":"Beauty","video":false,"overview":"Set in 1934, a black woman with mysterious abilities interviews to be the housekeeper to an eccentric white widow, but in order to get the job she must use her abilities in a way she didn't intend.","genre_ids":[18,14,10749],"popularity":1.6707,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"2018-05-09","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Beauty","original_language":"en"},{"id":8856,"adult":false,"title":"The Karate Kid Part II","video":false,"overview":"Summoned by his dying father, Miyagi returns to his homeland of Okinawa, with Daniel, after a 40-year exile. There he must confront Yukie, the love of his youth, and Sato, his former best friend turned vengeful rival. Sato is bent on a fight to the death, even if it means the destruction of their village. Daniel finds his own love in Yukia's niece, Kumiko, and his own enemy in Sato's nephew, the vicious Chozen. Now, far away from the tournaments, cheering crowds and safety of home, Daniel will face his greatest challenge ever when the cost of honor is life itself.","genre_ids":[12,18,28,10749,10751],"popularity":3.4369,"vote_count":2415,"poster_path":"/k0OwgRR6PNu7h3SiqpCbRdZWNaG.jpg","release_date":"1986-06-18","vote_average":6.335,"backdrop_path":"/7rfcRXbFD0xr8NteNq1hwXUd4Af.jpg","original_title":"The Karate Kid Part II","original_language":"en"},{"id":8867,"adult":false,"title":"The Punisher","video":false,"overview":"The avenging angel of Marvel Comics fame comes brilliantly to life in this searing action-adventure thriller! Dolph Lundgren stars as Frank Castle, a veteran cop who loses his entire family to a mafia car bomb. His ex-partner believes Castle survived the blast and became the Punisher, living in the sewers and exacting vigilante violence against mob bosses throughout the city. When the populace is caught in the midst of a gang war that he caused, Castle must again emerge from the shadows and save the innocent.","genre_ids":[28,80,18,53],"popularity":1.8603,"vote_count":653,"poster_path":"/tA0O0hYyHX7Hl2Fl8VEtGtfBtjI.jpg","release_date":"1989-10-05","vote_average":5.768,"backdrop_path":"/tFmrdnfXM0p6ihMTFpptYOKEfSl.jpg","original_title":"The Punisher","original_language":"en"},{"id":8840,"adult":false,"title":"DragonHeart","video":false,"overview":"In an ancient time when majestic fire-breathers soared through the skies, a knight named Bowen comes face to face and heart to heart with the last dragon on Earth, Draco. Taking up arms to suppress a tyrant king, Bowen soon realizes his task will be harder than he'd imagined: If he kills the king, Draco will die as well.","genre_ids":[14,28,12,18],"popularity":4.3924,"vote_count":2106,"poster_path":"/1J2FvxEoEKMFT9TjUdfhm0MJhZD.jpg","release_date":"1996-05-31","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/xbqluNfftDJtxDsqcpx9kKme4LF.jpg","original_title":"DragonHeart","original_language":"en"},{"id":277874,"adult":false,"title":"Kannedhirey Thondrinal","video":false,"overview":"Kannedhirey Thondrinal (transl. She appeared before my eyes) is a 1998 Indian Tamil-language romantic drama film directed by Ravichandran. The film stars Prashanth and Simran. The film's score and soundtrack were composed by Deva. The film's success later led to remakes in other languages as well.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"popularity":0.641,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/A8NIOLF1QVarZzO3A0TmIOHE36u.jpg","release_date":"1998-09-12","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/k2WA85TVGRcmXWdyhy5xal28XhG.jpg","original_title":"கண்ணெதிரே தோன்றினாள்","original_language":"ta"},{"id":8456,"adult":false,"title":"Never Back Down","video":false,"overview":"Jake, full of anger after his father's death, is just starting to find a place for himself at his new Orlando high school - until Ryan, head of an underground MMA fight club, picks Jake out as a prime opponent. After being trounced by Ryan in front of the entire school, Jake begins training under the firm, moral guidance of a MMA master, where he learns how to fight... and how to avoid a fight. But it becomes obvious that a rematch will be inevitable if Jake wants to stop Ryan and his bullying, once and for all.","genre_ids":[18,28],"popularity":4.968,"vote_count":2442,"poster_path":"/8oRUTyP1QAtGDMvRpKZyuyFPG0U.jpg","release_date":"2008-03-04","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/h71xyiurUscD6uIPbECyso1Lwb9.jpg","original_title":"Never Back Down","original_language":"en"},{"id":8471,"adult":false,"title":"Far North","video":false,"overview":"In the arctic, as Saiva is being born, a shaman declares that she is evil and will bring harm to all who become involved with her. Saiva is cast out of her tribe of herders and grows up to live a nomadic existence with Anja, a young woman she adopts as an infant. Then Loki, an injured and starving soldier, stumbles into their isolated lives. The women nurse him back to health, but treachery, violence and doom await them all.","genre_ids":[18,53,10749,80],"popularity":0.4282,"vote_count":56,"poster_path":"/d31sugp9MHWv7YHGxgM5iYQVmXB.jpg","release_date":"2008-10-09","vote_average":5.991,"backdrop_path":"/rOzQTb1CWIiRlDk8ILMULOSuktG.jpg","original_title":"Far North","original_language":"en"},{"id":8584,"adult":false,"title":"Shanghai Noon","video":false,"overview":"Chon Wang, a clumsy imperial guard, trails Princess Pei Pei when she's kidnapped from the Forbidden City and transported to America. Wang follows her captors to Nevada, where he teams up with an unlikely partner, outcast outlaw Roy O'Bannon, and tries to spring the princess from her imprisonment.","genre_ids":[12,28,35,37],"popularity":4.4939,"vote_count":2708,"poster_path":"/b0WwWRcDiDahkah5vZ0KjB4N9ZZ.jpg","release_date":"2000-05-26","vote_average":6.414,"backdrop_path":"/x4dH86KvLTGlIBMQb7kNTB0svy5.jpg","original_title":"Shanghai Noon","original_language":"en"},{"id":8585,"adult":false,"title":"My Beautiful Jinjiimaa","video":false,"overview":"My Beautiful Jinjiimaa is an emotional romantic drama in a setting few in the U.S. have ever seen. A deaf woman, Jinjiimaa, is raped by the local party Chairman, and shoots her attacker. Her lifelong friend, lame farmer Sukhee, goes to prison for six years for Jinjimaa’s crime. The film begins with his return, where Sukhee and Jinjiimaa meet—each with a secret.","genre_ids":[18,10749,10751],"popularity":0.1463,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/dV7YHWVkIoXtQmng1GDabf1MJ1K.jpg","release_date":"2003-03-07","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/ks4mPifdJO12lzzOqYFU3XoqU11.jpg","original_title":"Жинжиймаа","original_language":"mn"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt1853728","twitter_id":"unchainedmovie","facebook_id":"unchainedmovie","wikidata_id":"Q571032","instagram_id":null,"metacritic_id":"movie/django-unchained","mydramalist_id":"233288","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/django_unchained_2012"},"social_ids":{